        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Regional Impact of Disasters and Emergencies Relief Act or the RIDER Act</strong></p> <p>This bill expands eligibility for individual and public assistance to areas contiguous to an area designated as eligible to receive assistance as a result of a major disaster and includes cumulative damage from multiple natural catastrophes within the definition of major disaster.</p>]]>
        </text>
